{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给马叙伦的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给马叙伦的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年6月19日）马部长："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"另件奉还。此事宜速解决，要各校注意健康第一，学习第二。营养不足，宜酌增经费。学习和开会的时间宜大减。病人应有特殊待遇。全国一切学校都应如此。高教会已开过，中小两级宜各开一次。以上请考虑酌办。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此致敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月十九日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]马叙伦（1885—1970），字夷初，浙江杭县（今余杭）人。当时任中央人民政府委员、教育部部长。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":6,"day":19}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":502,"page_end":502},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}